import React from 'react' import ReactDOM from 'react-dom' import {add,sub,mul,div} from './Calc' ReactDOM.render( <>
  1. Sum of two number is {add(40,4)}
  2. Sub of two number is {sub(40,4)}
  3. Div of two number is {mul(40,4)}
  4. Mul of two number is {div(40,3)}
, document.getElementById('root') );
